10710073607/http://www.gaspirali.com/ksozluk/ A Comparative Dictionary of Turkic Languages] ''Open Project''\n* [http://turkic-languages.scienceontheweb.net/ The Turkic Languages in a Nutshell] with illustrations.\n* [http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Swadesh_lists_for_Turkic_languages Swadesh lists of Turkic basic vocabulary words] (from Wiktionary's [http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Appendix:Swadesh_lists Swadesh-list appendix])\n*[https://zenodo.org/record/3556954 Turkic basic vocabularies]\n* Conferences on Turkic languages processing: [https://web.archive.org/web/20150925132543/http://www.e-zerde.kz/zerde/index.php/ru/struktura-4/struktura-6 Astana, Kazakhstan, 2013], [http://www.turklang.itu.edu.tr/ Istanbul, Turkey, 2014], [https://web.archive.org/web/20150925133912/http://turklang.antat.ru/ Kazan, Tatarstan, 2015]\n\n{{-}}\n{{Turkic languages}}\n{{Turkic topics}}\n{{Altaic languages}}\n{{Language families}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Turkic Languages}}\n[[Category:Agglutinative languages]]\n[[Category:Language families]]\n[[Category:Turkic languages| ]]\n[[Category:History of Ural]]\n", "name_user": "Pauli133", "label": "safe", "comment": "no reason to <nowiki> those.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turkic_languages"}
